rows.label: tlk41100124_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Somebody beat my high score
in that Tiger! Tiger! game.
I was so shocked...

rows.label: tlk41100124_05_msg0003
rows.name:
But once I got over my shock,
I resolved to practice even harder.

rows.label: tlk41100124_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I trained from morning to night, never
stopping to eat, even when I got blisters
and my fingers started to bleed...

rows.label: tlk41100124_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Until finally, I achieved a new
high score of 81,107 points!

rows.label: tlk41100124_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Nobody's EVER going to beat this one.
I'm the top player in all of Alst!
